## Demo
![demo](.github/images/demo/demo.png)

## Usage

- Setup MQTT broker connection information
    heimdallr mqtt_token
- On computation machines run the publisher service.
    heimdallr publish
- Run server service on the displaying machine.
    heimdallr serve


